</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ESSENTIAL ROCK HAMMER: A must have, this 20oz hammer features rubberized grip for shock reduction; 11 inches in length and forged from one piece of steel, one side features a square face for hammering rock or driving chisels, while the opposing pointed tip allows you to crack open rocks or hard, dense material</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ROCKHOUNDING ACCESSORIES: Once you’ve made a mess in the field, you’re going to need to sort, examine and tidy up any new found materials; this kit includes a mini steel wire mesh classifier to screen off larger unwanted raw materials, examination brushes and a snifter bottle for more detailed cleaning work, plastic baggies and a magnification jewelers loupe</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DELUXE NYLON TOTE BAG: The deluxe nylon tool bag makes it easy to carry all your rockhounding tools to and from your field site, keeping everything organized; the tool bag features convenient side pockets, a durable lower compartment and large middle compartment</td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor 40pc Geology Rockhounding Kit with Mining Tools and Premium Carry Bag</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">169.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p><font face=\"Arial\">If rock hounding, gem hunting or finding fossils are your outdoor hobby or keen geological interest, you’ll need the right tools to set yourself up for success in the field!&nbsp;\n<br><font color=\"#0f1111\" style=\"\"><span style=\"white-space-collapse: collapse;\">All the included geology equipment and tools fit inside the spacious 16-inch heavy duty, 600D rip-stop nylon tool bag that is constructed with super tough, tear-resistant fabric for the strength and durability to carry your tools and haul out your found treasures and specimens. Featuring durable, heavy duty stitching with a large storage compartment, specifically designed for treasure hunting in all climates;&nbsp;</span></font><span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); white-space-collapse: collapse;\">our ASR Outdoor Deluxe Tool Bag will last you many seasons over an ordinary canvas equipment bag that will break a zipper and disintegrate in front of you.</span>&nbsp;</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">This rockhounding tools kit includes the following components:&nbsp;</font></p><ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); padding: 0px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Compact 2-in-1 shovel with pick; 20oz rock pick hammer; 3pc cold chisel set</font></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><font face=\"Arial\">6-inch coarse classifier rock screen; hand trowel with depth markers; mineral brushes</font></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Big beam LED-UV black light flashlight; aluminum collection jars with display lid</font></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Specimen identification mat; assorted clear specimen bags; magnification eye loupe; gem tweezers;</font></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Adjustable safety goggles; universal fit canvas work gloves; microfiber dust/debris rag</font></span></li></ul><p><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"color: rgb(15, 17, 17); white-space-collapse: collapse;\">You need the right tools to set yourself up for success in the field. If rock hounding and fossil hunting are your new hobby or a gift you are looking to give to create a passionate hobby or new, rewarding interest, you've found a curated collection that covers all your bases: breaking up deposits, collecting and sorting material, to cleaning and examining new found precious gems, rocks, minerals, and fossils<br></span>&nbsp;\nWhether you’re on the hunt for emeralds in North Carolina, for jade in Big Sur, California or fossils in Wyoming, this rockhounding kit from ASR Outdoor will have you organized and prepared for your next mineral mining adventure. Good luck!</font></p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2026</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t&nbsp;<table></table>\n\t</div>\n\n <center><br></center>",
